additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with skin. Do not use as a baby wipe or for personal hygiene. Hard surface disinfectant only. Not to be used on skin. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or doctor. If swallowed do not induce vomiting. Give a glass of water to drink. If skin contact occurs, wash thoroughly, if in eyes, wash out with large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. Not suitable for: Marbles, brass, copper, unfinished wood, carpet, fabrics, and unwaxed vinyl.
